{"tid":2254682,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"質疑阿十之死疑點多 遭懲教四協會譴責「發死人財」 邵家臻：反照自身刻毒","createTime":"2020-10-23T04:23:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T12:20:27.000Z","uid":48083,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4471be0d6265e9d54f8a82bbbfbaa35ba1b98b2e","tid":2254682,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T04:23:42.000Z","msg":"年初曾遭警暴的露宿者黎民十（阿十）本月初在小欖精神病治療所，被指「長褲纏頸自殺」身亡，立法會議員邵家臻、張超雄連日來質疑事件疑點重重。懲教署四個協會昨日發表聯合聲明，譴責邵家臻與張超雄連日發放「失實的信息抹黑」，批評是「發死人財」達到政治目的。邵家臻今早反駁，要求署方展示閉路電視片是希望釋除公眾疑慮，「為死去的阿十發聲竟被說成是『發死人財』？駡人者反照出自身的刻毒。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E9%98%BF%E5%8D%81%E4%B9%8B%E6%AD%BB%E7%96%91%E9%BB%9E%E5%A4%9A-%E9%81%AD%E6%87%B2%E6%95%99%E5%9B%9B%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC-%E7%99%BC%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%BA%E8%B2%A1-%E9%82%B5%E5%AE%B6%E8%87%BB-%E5%8F%8D%E7%85%A7%E8%87%AA%E8%BA%AB%E5%88%BB%E6%AF%92/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%2598%25BF%25E5%258D%2581%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%25A4%259A-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%2587%25B2%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%258D%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AD%25B4%25E8%25B2%25AC-%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B2%25A1-%25E9%2582%25B5%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%2587%25BB-%25E5%258F%258D%25E7%2585%25A7%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E5%2588%25BB%25E6%25AF%2592%2F&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FROSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=ba77f24e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%2598%25BF%25E5%258D%2581%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%25A4%259A-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%2587%25B2%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%258D%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AD%25B4%25E8%25B2%25AC-%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B2%25A1-%25E9%2582%25B5%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%2587%25BB-%25E5%258F%258D%25E7%2585%25A7%